_sText:
The best map of all time, I made it for 2 years. These locations, these walls... Studios such as Ubisoft, Electronic Arts and Blizzard will be shocked by the beauty of this location. Each new wall was made with soul. Each new window reminds me of the days when I woke up early in the morning in the village to the crowing of roosters.
Oh, do you want a joke? There was a bear, he did not live, saw a burning car and burned AHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHHAAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAH, oh ... oh ... oh ... I almost died laughing while writing this, the whole family laughed and my mother grunted like a pig that she had given birth to a new brother, ooh, how funny
